    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 981-generation Cayman S represents a pinnacle of mid-engine balance, powered by a naturally aspirated 3.4L flat-six engine that delivers 325 hp with a linear torque curve. Mated to a tactile 6-speed manual transmission, the drivetrain provides an engaging mechanical connection often lost in newer iterations. This example features Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) for variable damping and the Sport Chrono package for optimized throttle mapping. The chassis maintains its factory-spec structural rigidity, though the exterior shows minor road-derived patina. Recent maintenance includes a comprehensive cooling system refresh and a transaxle fluid service, ensuring the limited-slip differential and synchros operate with precision. The dual-mode sport exhaust provides a visceral flat-six howl, confirming the health of the valvetrain and exhaust scavenging system.",
      "price": 38500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
