      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle has been meticulously maintained and serves as a prime example of a well-cared-for daily driver. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, though a close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front bumper consistent with careful highway use. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and smoke-free; the leather seats remain supple with only light creasing on the driver\u2019s bolster. All electronic features, including the premium sound system and dual-zone climate control, function perfectly. Mechanically, the car is robust, with a comprehensive service history showing regular synthetic oil changes and a recent brake pad replacement. It shifts smoothly and handles with the precision you would expect from a vehicle of this caliber. This is a turn-key car ready for its next owner.",
      "price": 34500.0,
