      "description": "Available is a 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and an 8,000 RPM redline. This driver-focused example utilizes a 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory Variable M Differential. The chassis is robust, benefiting from proactive rear subframe reinforcement and a refreshed suspension setup with Bilstein dampers. The VANOS system is fully serviced for precise cam timing. While showing minor cosmetic wear typical of its age, the mechanical integrity is excellent, offering a raw, analog driving experience with communicative steering and a linear power band.",
